  My responsibility was to identify the root cause quickly.
  I analyzed logs in Splunk and traced the issue using Dynatrace.
  I found an inefficient database query causing the delay.
  I optimized the query and tested the fix thoroughly.
  After deployment, performance improved significantly.
  The issue was resolved within SLA with no business impact.

